item.title: Awesome Banana Bread
item.description: aka - Chocolate chip Pecan Oat Bran Banana Bread I workout a lot but I also have a sweet tooth. This is recipe I came up with as a way to have a healthier alternative to a more traditional banana bread. I am still tweaking this so it may change but I think it is rady to share. Growing up and far into my adult life my mom has made banana bread for my family and we usually finish it before it cools.

item.title: Hello World
item.description: Welcome to my new site! This is the first post on my new blog/website. I am building this website with hugo and using github pages for hosting. I am hoping to share information and personal opinions on coding, music, coffee, nutrition, and exercise.
